===== GIT INSTRUCTIONS =====
To begin, grab the newest version and merge it to your repository
$ git fetch upstream
$ git merge upstream/master

Next, make changes to files in the repository

Once done, add the everything to the commit list and commit
$ git add .
$ git commit -m "Comments for commit"

Finally, push the updates to the server
$ git push origin master

===== RUNNING INSTRUCTIONS =====
Open a command prompt and navigate to the game directory
Type ./wiimenu.py
to run the program 
